data.description: Step inside to the inviting foyer with original french doors leading to the living room, complete with a functional wood fireplace. The formal dining room flows into the family room, which has plenty of space for entertaining guests and a recently added sliding glass door for convenient access to the back yard. The recently updated kitchen includes a pantry and a half bath nearby. Upstairs, the master bedroom is massive and comes with dual closets, accompanied by three additional well sized bedrooms and a full bathroom with plenty of storage. The lower level has a finished second family room and an unfinished side that has space for storage and the washer and dryer. Behind the home you will find a fully fenced in backyard that includes a patio and a 1 stall garage with additional carport.
